mesquite.lib

Class MesquiteLong

  • java.lang.Object
    • mesquite.lib.MesquiteLong
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Listable

    public class MesquiteLong
extends java.lang.Object
implements Listable
    This long wrapper class is used to be able to pass integers by reference and have the original change as needed.
